1. *Učiš* li strane jezike? (Are you learning foreign languages?)
2. Da sam *učio* za ispit, ne bih pao. (If I had studied for the exam, I wouldn't have failed.)
3. Moram da *učim* još više kako bih bio bolji u svom poslu. (I need to study more in order to be better at my job.)
4. Kada *učiš* nešto novo, važno je da ostaneš fokusiran. (When you are learning something new, it is important to stay focused.)
5. *Učenik* je proveo sate *učeći* za test. (The student spent hours studying for the test.)
6. Ona *uči* da svira gitaru već nekoliko godina. (She has been learning to play the guitar for several years.)
7. Kada *učiš* neki strani jezik, najbolje je da se izložiš što više autentičnom govornom jeziku. (When learning a foreign language, it is best to expose yourself to as much authentic spoken language as possible.)
8. Njihova mama ih *uči* da budu pristojni i ljubazni prema drugima. (Their mother is teaching them to be polite and kind to others.)